reviews.text:
Not the best YTF I have had, and certainly not the worst. But it could be better, as one of the tofu tasted slightly stale, though the fish paste was okay.

The fried stuff were okay, but the display did attract quite a number of flies.  They need to figure out how to keep the flies away, perhaps by having an electric zapper mounted at the stall.

The lady staff was friendly, and the noodles were cooked al dente, which was good.;
